snippet.textDisplay: Okay guys listen up! This is gonna be long genuine and emotional 🥺. Our boys have come so far so frickin far, and I know that each and every one of us are so fucking proud of them and everything they’ve accomplished. These boys are our hope, our love, our voice and our 𝐄𝐯𝐞𝐫𝐲𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐧𝐠. They make us laugh and cry at the same time and I swear becoming an army was probably one of the best things I’ve ever done. Every time I watch edits, G.C.F’s or anything I start crying because all I can think about is how these baby birds grew up, spread their wings and soared the sky, falling many times. Finally they learned to fly and now here they are, the biggest kpop band in the world. Everything they have and everything that is coming their way...they deserve. They deserve it all. They’re talented at everything they do because they work hard for it. They truly are the best. Kim Namjoon, Kim Seokjin, Min Yoongi, Jung Hoseok, Park Jimin, Kim Taehyung and Jeon Jungkook. Our bullet proof boys. BTS always and Forever ❤️ ✊🏻 🧡 ✊🏼 💛 ✊ 💚 ✊🏽 💙 ✊🏾 💜 ✊🏿. So let’s make 2020 the best year ever and continue supporting from our hearts. KAPSAHAMNIDA and SARANGHAE
